## Helper Functions Reference

| Function | Purpose |
|---|---|
| `getNodeClassName(store, id)` | Read current `props.className` |
| `setNodeClassName(store, id, cls)` | Write `props.className` (normalises whitespace) |
| `patchNodeStyle(store, id, patch)` | Merge-patch `props.style`, removing empty-string keys |
| `getNodeStyle(store, id)` | Read current `props.style` |
| `replaceTokenGroup(cls, patterns, token)` | Replace a group of tokens with a new one (uses exact-token removal) |
| `removeExactToken(cls, token)` | Remove a specific token without touching compound tokens (e.g. removes `flex` without touching `flex-col`) |
| `replaceTwToken(cls, prefix, token)` | Replace a prefix-matched token |
| `removeTwToken(cls, prefix)` | Remove all tokens matching a prefix |
| `resolveColorClass(color, prefix)` | Map friendly names to CSS-variable Tailwind classes |
| `findNode(nodes, id)` | Deep-find a node by ID in the tree |

